### 3. Production Deployment

**GitHub Actions Setup:**
```bash
# Add the workflow file to your repo:
mkdir -p .github/workflows
cp scripts/github_actions_setup.py .github/workflows/personatrend-collection.yml
```

**API Keys Required:**
- NewsAPI: newsapi.org (free tier: 1000 requests/day)
- Reddit API: reddit.com/prefs/apps (free)
- Notion API: notion.so/my-integrations (free)
- Twitter API: developer.twitter.com (basic tier)
- Behance API: developer.adobe.com (optional, for design trends)

